title: You are invited to the Kentucky Environmental Justice Workshop. Pass it on! (City of Louisville, ...
text: ( Source : City of Louisville , KY) You are cordially invited to attend the 2015 Kentucky Environmental Justice Workshop on Friday, October 30 , 2015, at the University of Louisville Shelby Campus , Founders Union Building , 9001 Shelbyville Rd,
